{
  "stem": "1160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- in Hajdunanas, there was a sort of an industry, like straw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] knitting-- I think that's the word for it, knitting-- straw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wider ones, narrower ones, thicker ones, thinner ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from those straw-- they were doing it by the meter, and they were selling it by the meter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is what women in the evenings-- they were sitting outside and were talking, socializing-- and their hands were going and they were knitting it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from those straws, they were making hats, bags, slippers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were even making little mats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was traveling with this and he was selling it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was also selling, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember, candies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A lot of other things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't remember the other things, but the candies I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember my father coming back-- because he only came home for the weekends, was traveling all week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he likes to tease us children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] we had a-- we had a very big-- in this-- in this room, we had a bedroom, which was having two big cupboards, linen closets.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one was hanging clothes, and it was very tall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was against the wall, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the bed was close to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it had a headboard and it had a footboard also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because I was the youngest, and my siblings were telling me that I should stand up there, because top of the cupboard, there are candies.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were candy which, like-- like flat candies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can-- and a knife was on the top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have to cut it to get a piece from it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
